SUB_W07_EVAR_BOFO_MISSION_141_CUT_000_02.text:
Ah, you must be the Soul Voyager.
The temple told us you'd be coming;
we are excited to behold your success.

SUB_W07_EVAR_BOFO_MISSION_142_CUT_000_09.text:
I'm fine. But don't come any closer;
there may be evidence here that can
help us pin down the culprit.

SUB_W07_FUNC_BOFO_MISSIONCONFIRMATION_TE.text:
Thank you. I would like you to visit our farm;
its output is not increasing in quite the way
we had expected.

